edia_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1000" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/2c1f7730-14e5-11ee-b677-5734a388a08b" width="1600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Insta360]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The Insta360 Go 3 with its thumb-sized camera detached from its 'Action Pod' body for remote viewing.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Insta360 Go 3]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[TikTok is jumping off the BeReal bandwagon by killing TikTok Now]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>据<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/6/27/23775125/tiktok-now-discontinued-notification-bereal-murder-clone"><em>The Verge</em></a>报道，TikTok 已告诉用户，它将停止使用 TikTok Now，它实际上是去年轰动一时的社交媒体 BeReal 的克隆版。根据多位用户发布的截图，母公司字节跳动正在“更新 TikTok 体验并停止 TikTok Now”。</p><p> BeReal 是<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-be-real-apple-app-store-awards-121556627.html">苹果 2022 年年度 iPhone 应用程序</a>，但围绕这款社交媒体应用程序的热度最近逐渐减弱。与竞争对手相比，该应用程序采用了一种有趣的方法，每天在不同的时间发送通知，提示您同时快速分享使用设备的前置和后置摄像头拍摄的照片。我们的想法是创造更多自发的内容，同时保持以朋友为中心的体验。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> TikTok Now 采用了几乎相同的方法，也要求用户同时拍摄正面和背面照片。不过，它增加了拍摄 10 秒类似 TikTok 视频而不是照片的功能。该公司在推出时表示，其目标是“在 TikTok 上建立真实且自发的联系”。</p><p>该功能是美国主要应用程序的一部分，但在其他地区也可以作为独立的 TikTok Now 应用程序使用。发送给美国 TikTok 用户的消息表明，该功能正在主应用程序中被终止，但单独的 TikTok Now 应用程序没有任何消息。</p><p>推出后不久，BeReal 就获得了足够的成功，激发了 Instagram ( <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/instagram-bereal-candid-notes-172854546.html">Candid Stories</a> )、 <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/snapchat-dual-camera-130029031.html">SnapChat</a>等公司的双摄像头功能。然而，根据<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:The New York Times;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=c813ae39-7d58-41cb-ac66-ad830606ceef&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+New+York+Times&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJjODEzYWUzOS03ZDU4LTQxY2ItYWM2Ni1hZDgzMDYwNmNlZWYiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubnl0aW1lcy5jb20vMjAyMy8wNC8xMy9zdHlsZS9iZXJlYWwtYXBwLmh0bWwiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjlmYTUzZWE3LTgzZWQtNGIwZS05YTk3LTZiNTZmOWM4YjExOCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAa8EFYShXDCk_R7SGaxeZZVMd4qpEf7tnq-OVXKmzJga&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F04%2F13%2Fstyle%2Fbereal-app.html" class="rapid-with-clickid"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>四月份的报道，此后用户数量有所下降。不过，BeReal <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/bereal-says-it-has-more-than-20-million-daily-active-users-172721921.html">反驳了</a>该故事背后的<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://petapixel.com/2023/02/22/bereal-may-be-on-the-out-users-have-nearly-halved-since-peak/#:~:text=According%252520to%252520the%252520report%25252C%252520BeReal,3.3%252520million%252520in%252520January%2525202023.">分析报告</a>，称其仍拥有 2000 万每日活跃用户。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/tiktok-is-jumping-off-the-bereal-bandwagon-by-killing-tiktok-now-125023950.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/tiktok-is-jumping-off-the-bereal-bandwagon-by-killing-tiktok-now-125023950.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9fa53ea7-83ed-4b0e-9a97-6b56f9c8b118</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫·登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 12:50:23 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687870225</ingested><modified> 2023-06-27T12:50:30+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Small Businesses]]></category><category><![CDATA[Software]]></c