眩光困扰的房间。然而，与大多数三星电视一样，它不支持杜比视界 HDR。三星已用<a data-i13n="cpos:57;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwQlRUVkw0MTk_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMTRhLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3OTE3YzIyYS03ODg5LTRjMzItYTJkOS05NWFhY2RhMWQyMTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAYY0-v-7BpJ80AHDhOfZpIYC2NtEvwBGcRoIPAOpR_as&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BTTVL419">新的 QN90C</a>取代了这款 2022 年型号，但该套件的 55 英寸版本目前价格高出 600 美元，因此 QN90B 暂时仍然具有更高的价值。</p><h2>三星 Galaxy Watch 5 </h2><p><core-commerce id="82b39bb57d2e41dab1c787229046a5f2" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:58;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEIySjVUQjNRP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE0YS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNzkxN2MyMmEtNzg4OS00YzMyLWEyZDktOTVhYWNkYTFkMjExIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAWiQntQfuL-DpTNEDx9m5QPh_cN-L6WPbhTNq0SxIGRo&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B2J5TB3Q">三星 Galaxy Watch 5</a> 40 毫米型号降至 229 美元， <a data-i13n="cpos:59;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEIySjRXNVRUP3RoPTEmdGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMTRhLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3OTE3YzIyYS03ODg5LTRjMzItYTJkOS05NWFhY2RhMWQyMTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAU1TmQmGcWLZhjXtQLGpqR2ggaG5X4r_eZuqNKt3fF-7&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B2J4W5TT%3Fth%3D1">44 毫米型号</a>降至 259 美元。这两笔交易均创下历史新低，但均距迄今为止的最佳价格不到 10 美元。去年我们给 Galaxy Watch 5 <a data-i13n="cpos:60;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-watch-5-pro-review-battery-life-specs-durability-180052187.html">的评分为 85 分</a>，目前它是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:61;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-smartwatches-153013118.html">智能手表购买指南</a>中“最适合 Android 用户”的选择。虽然它的电池寿命可能会更长，但它的设计耐用且有吸引力，它的操作系统易于导航，而且它的健康跟踪相对全面。不过，三星预计将在未来几周内发布<a data-i13n="cpos:62;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-watch-6-leak-suggests-the-rotating-bezel-will-return-124637657.html">Galaxy Watch 6</a> ，因此，如果您现在不需要新的智能手表，那么可能值得等待，看看该型号的表现如何。</p><h2> Google Pixel 7a + Pixel Buds A 系列</h2><p><core-commerce id="bc03f3966efb4f8381f72684ce1d5060" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>亚马逊将包括<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:63;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAUEmoHTd7IM41V8YPjc4ugbl9KKmEQ5JFRVAtyp_zVOe&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGoogle-Pixel-7a-128GB-Charcoal-Pixel%2Fdp%2FB0C7WB7FGS" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/Google-Pixel-7a-128GB-Charcoal-Pixel/dp/B0C7WB7FGS?" class="rapid-with-clickid">Google Pixel 7a 智能手机和 Pixel Buds A-Series 在内</a>的捆绑包降价 100 美元，降至 499 美元。如果您需要手机升级但又不想花很多钱，那么这是一个很棒的捆绑包。 Pixel 7a 是您目前可以获得的<a data-i13n="cpos:64;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-engadget-guide-to-the-best-midrange-smartphones-120050366.html">最佳中端手机</a>，这要归功于其快速的 Tensor G2 芯片组、流畅的 90Hz 显示屏、IP67 防水性能、出色的摄像头和对无