03-firewatch-team-pauses-its-next-game-to-work-on-valve-titles.html"><em>看火人</em></a></ins>和<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-quarry-game-release-date-201557551.html"><em>直到天亮</em></a></ins>。 Fallen Leaf 指出，游戏的故事情节没有镜头切换或加载屏幕，“可以在一场紧张的游戏中沉迷其中”。如果不出意外的话，<em>索利斯堡</em>应该是一个技术展示中心。旁边<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/layers-of-fear-gameplay-footage-takes-you-on-a-tour-of-a-gorgeous-creepy-lighthouse-172058956.html"><em>层层恐惧</em></a></ins>，这是自 Epic 首次展示该技术以来首批推出的虚幻引擎 5 游戏之一<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/epic-games-unreal-engine-5-demo-150044561.html">回到2020年</a></ins>。 <em>《索利斯要塞》</em>将在 PlayStation 5、PC（通过 Steam 和 Epic Games Store）和<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-silicon-macs-now-natively-support-unreal-engine-5-124257710.html">苹果</a></ins>。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="67c98547e8f9456da54058c82fb5ff81"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OBcZGqXv6lE?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/sci-fi-thriller-fort-solis-arrives-on-playstation-5-pc-and-mac-on-august-22nd-191021189.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/sci-fi-thriller-fort-solis-arrives-on-playstation-5-pc-and-mac-on-august-22nd-191021189.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 6d4260ad-2b36-437a-a727-4aa18d67c768</guid><dc:creator>伊戈尔·博尼法西奇</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 26 Jun 2023 19:10:21 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687831956</ingested><modified> 2023-06-27T02:12:39+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|